<h1>Future Prospects - Payment Failed</h1>

<p><%= @student.full_name %>,</p>

<p>This email is to inform you that we were unable to take the following payment using the supplied payment details.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Amount: <strong><%= number_to_currency @payment.amount_pounds, unit: 'Â£' %></strong></li>
  <li>Description: <strong><%= @payment.description %></strong></li>
  <li>Payment Type: <strong><%= @payment.payment_type.humanize %></strong></li>
  <li>Payment Date: <strong><%= format_date @payment.paid_at %></strong></li>
  <% if @payment.credit_card? %>
    <li>Card Holder: <strong><%= @payment.card_holder %></strong></li>
    <li>Card Number: <strong><%= credit_card_number @payment.last_four_digits %></strong></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>

<p>Your application cannot be processed until this payment is received. You have
  <strong><%= Application::PAYMENT_EXPIRY_DAYS %> days</strong> to make a successful payment.</p>
<p>This means we must receive a payment from you by <strong><%= format_date @payment.application.payment_expiry_time %></strong>.</p>

<p>In order to make a payment, please <%= link_to 'sign in', root_url %> to the Future Prospects site and use
  the make payment option.</p>

<p>Sincerely,
  <br><br>
  Future Prospects</p>
